quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,73,"Then look how was the end of those who were warned -"
  37,74,"But not the chosen servants of Allāh."
  37,75,"And Noah had certainly called Us, and [We are] the best of responders."
  38,52,"And with them will be women limiting [their] glances{1} and of equal age.",footnotes:1:To their mates alone.
  38,53,"This is what you, [the righteous], are promised for the Day of Account."
  38,54,"Indeed, this is Our provision; for it there is no depletion."
  39,37,"And whoever Allāh guides - for him there is no misleader. Is not Allāh Exalted in Might and Owner of Retribution?"
  39,38,"And if you asked them, ",footnotes:1:i.e., "Tell me about..."
  39,39,"Say, "
  40,16,"The Day they come forth nothing concerning them will be concealed from Allāh. To whom belongs [all] sovereignty this Day? To Allāh, the One, the Prevailing.{1}",footnotes:1:Refer to footnotes in 12:39.
  40,17,"This Day every soul will be recompensed for what it earned. No injustice today! Indeed, Allāh is swift in account."
  40,18,"And warn them, [O Muḥammad], of the Approaching Day, when hearts are at the throats, filled [with distress]. For the wrongdoers there will be no devoted friend and no intercessor [who is] obeyed."